{"arkId":"cl010111609","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010111609","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Tabati\u00e8re ovale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Tabati\u00e8re ovale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XVI (1774-1792) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1777","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 628 - Cabinet de Marie-Antoinette, Vitrine 2B","room":"Salle 628, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1777,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"2e moiti\u00e9 du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"M\u00e9ni\u00e8re , Paul-Nicolas","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"vers 1746","place":"","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1826","place":"","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q16889561"},{"label":"Welper, Jean-Daniel","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"vers 1729","place":"Strasbourg","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1789","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Miniaturiste","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q66762494"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 6850","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Tabati\u00e8re de forme ovale en or cisel\u00e9 et \u00e9mail couleur \u0022prune\u0022. La boite est d\u00e9cor\u00e9e de 4 pilastres avec bustes de femmes et 4 bas-reliefs en or mat sous verre qui repr\u00e9sentent les arts lib\u00e9reaux (Musique, Peinture, Sculpture, Astronomie). Ils sont encadr\u00e9s d\u0027\u00e9mail de couleur verte et de lauriers d\u0027or. Il en va de m\u00eame pour la miniature au milieu du couvercle. Cette miniature, que l\u0027on pense faite au pastel, repr\u00e9sente Louis XVI d\u0027apr\u00e8s un portrait de Joseph-Siffred Duplessis. Le roi est tout juste \u00e2g\u00e9 de 21 ans sur cette repr\u00e9sentation. Il est habill\u00e9 de v\u00eatements ordinaires mais d\u00e9cor\u00e9 de ses distinctions militaires, notamment la croix de l\u0027ordre de la Toison d\u0027Or.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Lettre N (1776 - 1777) (Poin\u00e7on de maison commune : sur le revers du couvercle et le revers de la b\u00e2te)\r ; Monogramme de Paris (1775 - 1781) (Poin\u00e7on de charge : sur le revers du couvercle et sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)\r ; Poin\u00e7on de ma\u00eetre orf\u00e8vre (sur le revers du couvercle, sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)\r ; T\u00eate de singe (1775 - 1781) (Poin\u00e7on de d\u00e9charge : sur la gorge)\r ; Signature : \r ; \u0022Menierre Rue Moncomseille \u00e0 Paris\u0022 (sur la gorge)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,5","displayDimension":"3,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"8,4","displayDimension":"8,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"6,4","displayDimension":"6,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or (\u00e9maill\u00e9)\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection baron Basile de Schlichtin